t's the good stuff actually getting in. The result is a foundational glow that lasts for days, not minutes.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXonGk17jK_label","label":"ggXonGk17jK_label","default":"<p>Try the Nifora Bio-Collagen Mask Today</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggT7QwNFaa8_text","label":"ggT7QwNFaa8_text","default":"And it’s not just me.."},{"type":"html","id":"ggT877IUNv4_text","label":"ggT877IUNv4_text","default":"<p>After my first experience, I was still curious. I thought my results might be just a one-time thing, so I did what we all do: I went online to read the reviews.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>And it turns out...</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I'm not the only one having this 'game-changer' moment. Seeing these comments from other women sealed the deal for me.</p>"}],
